data.description: You are home when you walk into this amazing single story open floor plan home with gorgeous hardwood floors. The beautiful kitchen with large island overlooks the dining room and spacious living room with lots of windows flooding the room with natural light. It is perfect for entertaining a few people or a crowd with space to spare.  Just down the hall you have a great office space, half bath and two nice sized bedroom sharing a jack and jill.  On the other side of the living you have full bath, guest room and a great game or media room.  Opposite side of the house you find the owner retreat with ensuite, separate vanities, soaking tub, large shower, walk in closet connected to the laundry room with sink that leads to the mud room and 3 car garage. Your oversized covered patio has a built in grill with fridge and space for ice to keep the drinks cool.  Want to add a pool, sports court or whatever you like well you have the space this home is on an acre.
